discussion_comments.comment_body: :( I think we should rename this to `MongoDBAtlasOrganizationUpdateProperties`.
this name collides with the namespace of another RP, we should rename it.
this is very likely to collide with system types, we need to specify its name

we need a better name than this `ConnectorData` - this is quite generic.
We need to add a `@@clientName` in your spec to rename this model to a more verbose name.
Per rules in the .net generator, the corresponding resource and collection class will change accordingly.

this is also generic, we need a more verbose name for this type.
Usually for this kind of models, we just prepend the RP name `ImpactReporting` to it so that we have `ImpactReportingErrorDetailProperties`.
